---
description: Approve a spec_ready feature so implementation can begin.
argument-hint: "<feature-slug>"
allowed-tools: Read, Edit, Bash
---

A human is approving the spec for `$ARGUMENTS`. Confirm that `specs/$ARGUMENTS/` contains `requirements.md`, `design.md`, and `tasks.md`, then mark the feature `approved` and set it `in_progress` in `feature_list.json` so the `implementer` can start.

If the spec is incomplete or ambiguous, say exactly what is missing instead of approving.
